spec_data.Name: maven-wagon
spec_data.Description:
Maven Wagon is a transport abstraction that is used in Maven's
artifact and repository handling code. Currently wagon has the
following providers:
* File
* HTTP
* FTP
* SSH/SCP
* WebDAV
* SCM (in progress)
